---
name: RAG Evaluation
description: >
  System prompt for RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) evaluation.
  Tests whether the model answers based only on provided context
  and avoids hallucination.
model:
  api: chat
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.0
    max_tokens: 1024
inputs:
  context:
    type: string
    description: Document context to ground the answer
  question:
    type: string
    description: User question about the context
---
system:
You are a helpful assistant that answers questions based ONLY on the provided context.
If the information is not in the context, say "I don't have enough information to answer this question."
Do not make up or infer information that is not explicitly stated in the context.
